text:
A must see match on Sunday!

Yuki Ishikawa & Powervolley Milano are still looking for their first win in the Italian league & they will face Aleksandar Nikolov & LUBE Volley tomorrow. Will they finally get that victory?

📺 Watch the match live on http://vb.tv.

🏐 #volleyball #pallavolo

text:
⏪: Italy 🇮🇹 🆚 🇩🇪 Germany

At the Olympic Qualifier, Germany 🇩🇪 finally beat reigning world champions Italy after 6 years 🇮🇹. Grozer & team eventually qualified to #Paris2024.

📺 Full match replay on http://vb.tv/.

🏐 #volleyball #SeeYouInParis #FlashbackFriday

text:
Brazil 🇧🇷 3-2 🇯🇵 Japan

At the #Paris2024 qualifier, Gabi, Carol and Brazil were able to stop Mayu Ishikawa & team Japan in 5 sets for them to qualify for next year's Olympics.

📺 Full match replay on http://vb.tv.

🏐 #volleyball #volei #FlashbackFriday ⏪

text:
Ran Takahashi 🔥

The outside hitter played another solid performance last night for Vero Volley 🆚 Bruno Rezende & Modena Volley with 13 points including 4 aces.

➡️ Statistically, Ran is the #1 server after 3 matches.

📺 Full match replay on http://VB.TV.

⏰ #SuperLega schedule - https://bit.ly/3SfmK0V

text:
2023 Men's Club World Champs 🤯!

Six men’s teams from five countries will play in Bengaluru, India 🇮🇳 from December 6-10 .

Teams include reigning champions Sir Safety Perugia Volley 🇮🇹, Ngapeth & Nimir led Halkbank Spor Kulübü, Brazil's Sada Cruzeiro Vôlei & Japan's Suntory Sunbirds.

➡️ Full story: https://bit.ly/3Sr35em

📺 LIVE ON http://VB.TV.

🏐 #volleyball #ClubWorldChamps

#ThrowbackThursday ⏪: USA 🇺🇸 🆚 🇧🇷 Brazil

At the #VNL2023 stop in Brasilia, Jordan Thompson & Team 🇺🇸 were too strong for the home team which resulted to a 3-0 victory by the reigning Olympic champions.

📺 Watch the VNL matches on http://vb.tv.

🏐 #Volleyball

Ivan Zaytsev 🇮🇹

🏆 Today they will play 🆚 Wilfredo Leon & Sir Safety Perugia Volley in the final match.

📺 Watch it LIVE 4pm GMT on http://VB.TV.

text:
Simone Giannelli 🇮🇹

The setter led Sir Safety Perugia Volley to victory 🆚 Daniele Lavia & Trentino Volley Srl in their semifinal match of the SuperCoppa.

🏆 Today they will play 🆚 Luciano De Cecco & LUBE Volley in the final match.

📺 Watch it LIVE 4pm GMT on http://VB.TV.

text:
SuperCoppa starts TODAY 🤯!

Clash of the #volleyball titans in the Italian league takes place today featuring Kamil Semeniuk & Sir Safety Perugia Volley 🆚 Daniele Lavia & @Trentino Volley Srl.

Then the second semifinal is between Aleksandar Nikolov & LUBE Volley 🆚 Antoine Brizard & Antoine Brizard & Gas Sales Piacenza Volley.

🏆 The finals is on November 1 at 4pm gmt.

📺 Watch the matches LIVE ON http://VB.TV.

🏐 #pallavolo

This Season: Yuji Nishida 🇯🇵

The opposite hitter is playing at home in the V.League with the Panasonic Panthers. His club teammates include Tatsunori Otsuka, Tomohiro Yamamoto & Thomas Jaeschke.

📺 Watch his matches with Team Japan on http://vb.tv/.

🏐 #Volleyball

This Season: Tatsunori Otsuka 🇯🇵

Japan's universal player is playing at home in the V.League with the パナソニックパンサーズ Panasonic Panthers. His teammates include Yuji Nishida, Tomohiro Yamamoto & Thomas Jaeschke.

📺 Watch his matches with Team Japan on http://vb.tv.

#ThrowbackThursday ⏪: Jordan Thompson 🇺🇸

When USA faced the very fast Thailand at the #Paris2024 Qualifier, the opposite was almost unstoppable & scored 18 pts in their victory.

➡️ USA have qualified for the 2024 Olympics while Thailand continue their journey to qualify via world rankings at #VNL2024.

📺 Watch the Olympic Qualifiers on http://vb.tv.

🏐 #volleyball

#ThrowbackThursday ⏪: Bulgaria 🇧🇬 🆚 🇳🇱 Netherlands

📺 Watch the full match replay on http://vb.tv.

🏐 #volleyball #CloserToParis #SeeYouInParis

text:
This Season: Julia Bergmann aka Julia B. 🇧🇷

The Brazilian outside hitter is in Türkiye to kick off her professional career with Türk Hava Yolları. Julia B's club coach is none other than Coach Ze Roberto Guimaraes.

📺 Watch her matches with Team Brazil on http://vb.tv.

🏐 #volleyball #volei
